---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn what QuizNiva is and how it helps beginner learners practice."
  currentPath="/about"
>
  <section class="page-intro section">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Focused Study Practice</h1>
    <p>
      QuizNiva is a free learning site for short notes, examples, MCQs, and answer explanations. The first course is Python beginner practice.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section prose prose--standalone">
    <h2>Who This Site Is For</h2>
    <p>
      This site is for students and self-learners who want a simple path through beginner topics. Each topic is designed to be read quickly, practiced immediately, and reviewed through explanations.
    </p>

    <h2>How The Content Works</h2>
    <p>
      Every finished topic has a lesson page and a quiz page. The lesson explains the idea with examples and common mistakes. The quiz checks understanding and shows explanations after submission.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
